      "title": "Sri Lankan Minister goes to CID against CPC",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekara said that he filed a complaint with the CID to investigate the activities at the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation, and the Ceylon Petroleum Storage Terminals Limited (CPSTL).",
        "Kanchana Wijesekera has requested to investigate Fuel procurement, Evaluation of proposals, Non-placement of orders, Selection of suppliers, Delays in payments, Distribution irregularities & Allegations made by individuals against the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation, and the Ceylon Petroleum Storage Terminals Limited (CPSTL).",
        "President to visit Japan next month to hold talks on debt restructuring"
      ],
